title.narrative: EAPR has strengthened evidence, partnerships and resource mobilization capacity to improve NUTRITION outcomes.

description.narrative: In 2021, EAPRO Nutrition aimed to enhance the impact of UNICEF Nutrition programmes through effective evidence generation, resource mobilization, and partnerships.;The Section created novel evidence to protect the diets, services practices that are essential for Nutrition. It further solidified its partnerships with UN partners, the ASEAN Secretariat, and leading universities while attempting new engagements with influencers. Aided by evidence generation and partnership, EAPRO successfully helped launch Global Action Plan on Wasting Roadmaps and attracted new regional resource partners. | Status:Met | As-of Date:15/03/2022
